@startuml
title PDE Physical Chain - Single SLM/Camera Capture Sequence (Development Mode)

actor "Application" as App
participant "PDEPhysicalChain\n(Main Thread)" as PDE
participant "Worker\nThread" as Worker
participant "SLMController\n(Singleton)" as SLM
box "Hardware" #LightBlue
participant "SLM\nHardware" as SLM_HW
end box
participant "Camera" as Cam
participant "Frame Grabber\n(DMA Pool)" as DMA
participant "Frame\n(RAII)" as Frame

note over PDE : State: Ready\n(acquisition started,\nDMA buffers allocated)
note over SLM : Single SLM mode\n(dev/test configuration)

== Capture Request ==
App -> PDE : setSLMCaptureCamera\n(slm_data, nullptr)
activate PDE
note right of PDE : State: Ready → First_SLM_write

PDE -> Worker : executeOnWorker\n(lambda with SDK calls)
activate Worker
note right of Worker : All SDK access\nserialized here\n(SDK not thread-safe)

== Write SLM ==
Worker -> SLM : writeImage(SLM, data)
activate SLM
note right of SLM : PCIe DMA\n(~1ms)
SLM -> SLM_HW : DMA transfer
activate SLM_HW
SLM --> Worker : DMA complete
deactivate SLM

Worker -> SLM : ImageWriteComplete(SLM)
activate SLM
note right of SLM : Wait for SLM\nto stabilize
SLM_HW -> SLM_HW : pixel flip\n+ settling\n(~1ms)
SLM_HW --> SLM : stable
SLM --> Worker : image stable
deactivate SLM

note right of PDE : State: First_SLM_write\n→ Capture

== Hardware Trigger from SLM ==
SLM_HW -> Cam : **Hardware Trigger Pulse**\n(from SLM output)
deactivate SLM_HW

note right of Cam : Built-in delay\nconfigured via\nsetTriggerDelay()\nensures SLM settled

== Camera Capture (Zero-Copy) ==
Worker -> Cam : grabFrameZeroCopy()
activate Cam
Cam -> DMA : capture to pool
activate DMA
note right of DMA : DMA to buffer\n(locks one buffer)
DMA --> Cam : ScopedBuffer
deactivate DMA

Cam -> Frame ** : create Frame\n(unique_ptr<ScopedBuffer>)
activate Frame
note right of Frame : Ownership transfer:\nDMA buffer → Frame\n(RAII pattern)

Cam --> Worker : Frame
deactivate Cam

Worker --> PDE : CaptureResult\n{camera1_frame}
deactivate Worker

note right of PDE : State: Capture → Ready\n(ready for next capture)

PDE --> App : CaptureResult
deactivate PDE

== Frame Processing ==
activate App
note right of App : Application owns Frame\n(zero-copy access)

App -> Frame : getData(), process()
activate Frame
Frame --> App : void* (DMA buffer)
deactivate Frame

note right of App : Process image

App -> App : Frame destroyed\n(goes out of scope)
deactivate App

destroy Frame
note right of Frame : RAII destructor:\nReleases buffer\nback to DMA pool

note over DMA : Buffer available\nfor next capture

@enduml
